Roar,Engine,is,a,platform,that,gives,users,the,ability,to,quickly,build,social,games,and,monetize,them,It,lets,users,create,social,game,mechanics,using,core,building,blocks,that,can,be,combined,to,build,a,range,of,popular,and,custom,gameplay,systems,The,Roar,API,lets,users,access,the,meta,data,and,game,logic,The,API,uses,HTTP,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML